    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5bu1gvholjbm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 195,
      "strokeColor": "#1a1a1a",
      "text": "1. Cold Launch",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.247Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.247Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5b7wq77rwyal",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 230,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "• App icon → splash\n• No Fitz persisted (@State only,\n  per D-2026-05-19-002, Casey M7)\n• No lastUV? jump to disclaimer\n• Has cached UV? still gated by L1",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.247Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.247Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5bf9wxxdq22h",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 380,
      "y": 180,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 280,
      "backgroundColor": "#FFCDD2",
      "strokeColor": "#C62828",
      "strokeWidth": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.247Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.247Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5cjkaj24dla8c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 400,
      "y": 195,
      "strokeColor": "#B71C1C",
      "text": "2. L1 Disclaimer (.fullScreenCover)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.248Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.248Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5dtraol2y90e8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 400,
      "y": 230,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "• Title: \"How accurate is this for you?\"\n• Body + ⚠️ glyph (Donatello M1)\n• Children-line on its own row\n• Inline \"see About\" → notForMe anchor\n• Photosensitizer line above the fold\n• Button: \"I understand\" (single CTA)\n• Re-fires EVERY cold launch\n• NO \"Don't Show Again\"",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.249Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.249Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5dlhdp80fvoh",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 180,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 280,
      "backgroundColor": "#E3F2FD",
      "strokeColor": "#0D47A1",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.249Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.249Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5d1f1uvhgv1ky",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 720,
      "y": 195,
      "strokeColor": "#0D47A1",
      "text": "3. Skin-Type Picker (Fitz)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.249Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.249Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5dw0mzqefr9oe",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 720,
      "y": 230,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "• Header: \"Pick the row that matches\n  what your skin DOES, not its color\"\n• Rows I–VI, each ≥56pt tap target\n• ❌ NO default selection (D-...-012)\n• ❌ NO skin-tone swatches (MMT-3)\n• Wheeler edited variant copy:\n  I \"Very fair…\", II \"Fair…\", III\n  \"Medium tone…\", IV \"Light-brown…\",\n  V \"Brown… rarely burns\", VI\n  \"Deeply pigmented… never burns\"\n• Cite in About: NCBI NBK481857 +\n  Fitzpatrick 1988 (paraphrase only,\n  D-2026-05-19-009 ✅)\n• @State only — never @AppStorage",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.249Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.249Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5egte08kezq",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 1020,
      "y": 180,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 280,
      "backgroundColor": "#E3F2FD",
      "strokeColor": "#0D47A1",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5e4og5d8reh48",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1040,
      "y": 195,
      "strokeColor": "#0D47A1",
      "text": "4. Location Permission",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5etv07gv3ear",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1040,
      "y": 230,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "• Inline rationale BEFORE iOS prompt\n• \"When-In-Use\" only (never \"Always\")\n• Privacy line: rounded coords sent to\n  Apple Weather; only last rounded\n  coordinate may be saved on device\n• Primary CTA: \"Use my location\"\n  in .safeAreaInset(.bottom) — thumb\n• On deny → graceful empty state,\n  not error string. Re-tap path.\n• Required because WeatherKit needs\n  location for currentWeather UV\n  (D-2026-05-19-003)\n• SPF picker also shown here (chip\n  row, neutral, default SPF 30)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5ez3aezuhn8ip",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 1340,
      "y": 180,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 280,
      "backgroundColor": "#FFF9C4",
      "strokeColor": "#F57F17",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5eojgeoarwgol",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1360,
      "y": 195,
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "text": "5. Photo-Sens Awareness",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5e6h9xvprcytq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1360,
      "y": 230,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "⚠ NOT a separate screen — three\n   surfaces (per Wheeler §7.3):\n\n(a) Inside L1 modal (step 2):\n    inline \"see About\" → notForMe\n(b) L3 link on verdict card (next):\n    \"Is this estimate for me?\"\n(c) L4 About section, anchor =\n    notForMe (Wheeler-authored)\n\n❌ NO \"I'm photosensitive\" toggle\n   (zero special-category data,\n   per Raphael Art.9 / Casey M7)\n❌ NO brand drug names — generics\n   only (Plunder)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5e3klzbaya22u",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 1660,
      "y": 180,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 280,
      "backgroundColor": "#C8E6C9",
      "strokeColor": "#1B5E20",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5epkv4k0keaej",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1680,
      "y": 195,
      "strokeColor": "#1B5E20",
      "text": "6. First Verdict ↓ Main",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd5e5e0wbu6tlhqb2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1680,
      "y": 230,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "• Hero number animates in\n  (.contentTransition(.numericText))\n• Tier badge color+shape+symbol\n• L2 footer becomes visible\n• L3 link \"Is this estimate for me?\"\n  becomes reachable\n• WeatherKit lockup visible\n• Success haptic (.sensoryFeedback)\n• Lands on NowView (= Main Screen\n  below, in LANE 2)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:20:49.250Z",
      "version": 1
    },
