    {
      "id": "mpcdb7k7jp61iv1z7gp",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1680,
      "y": 145,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "Screen fills (LANE 1):\n  ░ light gray   = neutral system screen (splash, verdict)\n  ░ red          = L1 disclaimer (mandatory acknowledgment)\n  ░ light blue   = system task screen (Fitz, location)\n  ░ yellow       = passive moment (no separate screen)\n  ░ green        = success / first verdict landing\n\nSub-regions (LANE 2 — Main Screen):\n  ░ green        = verdict card / hero\n  ░ light blue   = inputs + timer\n  ░ purple       = WeatherKit attribution\n  ░ orange       = window-elapsed / re-attestation\n  ░ gray         = L2 footer (inert)\n  ░ pink         = Settings/About entry → L4 anchor\n\nArrows:  solid blue = primary linear flow\n         solid orange = annotation pointer\n         (no dashed arrows used in this diagram)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:25:20.647Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:25:20.647Z",
      "version": 1
