      "x": 215,
      "y": 2295,
      "strokeColor": "#B71C1C",
      "text": "~10–15 sec STICKY.\nDoing gear-weight\nmath. Reads whole\ndisclaimer. Will not\ntap inline link (not\nphoto-sens'd). May\nscreenshot.",
