    {
      "id": "mpcde2s35rh5bi7anio",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 220,
      "y": 2395,
      "strokeColor": "#4A148C",
      "text": "★ LOAD-BEARING ★  30–60 sec dwell.\nSees photo-sens line → TAPS \"see About\"\ninline → AboutView opens at notForMe\nanchor (on top of L1) → reads cohort list\n→ recognizes \"retinoids\" = her Accutane\n→ dismisses → returns to L1 → \"I understand\"\nTHIS IS THE VISIBILITY LOOP (not attestation).",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s3yla4bzh9r2b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 475,
      "y": 2395,
      "strokeColor": "#4A148C",
      "text": "Picks Fitz IV (her\nactual phototype).\nRE-READS footer:\n\"assumes healthy skin\n+ no photo-sens meds\"\n— even though she\nalready saw L1.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s3witigs1b6gs",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 735,
      "y": 2395,
      "strokeColor": "#4A148C",
      "text": "Reads privacy ¶\n(medical-privacy\nposture). Grants\nreluctantly. Never\n\"Always\" location.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
