    {
      "id": "mpcde2s396iis1d7hmw",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 995,
      "y": 2395,
      "strokeColor": "#4A148C",
      "text": "★ MOST IMPORTANT L3 TAP IN THE APP ★\nVerdict reads \"120 min\" but lived\nexp says ~20 min. TAPS L3 \"Is this\nestimate for me?\" → AboutView notForMe.\nMentally divides 120 by 4–6. Quote:\n\"UV maybe 3 and it looks like I've\nrolled a few. What can I do to stop this?\"",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s3ybeuwqinfp9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1255,
      "y": 2395,
      "strokeColor": "#4A148C",
      "text": "★ L1 re-fires every\ncold launch = HER\nre-attestation surface\nwhen meds change.\nWhy Donatello M1 says\nNO \"Don't Show Again.\"",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s3ubvx4a9s7th",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1515,
      "y": 2395,
      "strokeColor": "#4A148C",
      "text": "Probably indoors by\nthis point (her cohort\nburns at 5 min of\ngardening). Reads\nelapsed copy as\nratification.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
