    {
      "id": "mpcde2s5bzf8q1pnfp",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 75,
      "y": 2498,
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "text": "P5  TOMÁS\ntrail runner\nr/trailrunning\nFitz IV/V",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s5py3ztuzq56d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 215,
      "y": 2495,
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "text": "~2 sec RISK.\nOne earbud in, at\ntrailhead. Dismisses\nwithout reading.\nL2 footer must\ndo real work for\nhim every screen.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s5g0ro78ujv3b",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 465,
      "y": 2490,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 86,
      "backgroundColor": "#FFF3E0",
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "strokeWidth": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s5oyk9cjpcr3c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 475,
      "y": 2495,
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "text": "⚠ UNDER-PICK RISK\nActually Fitz IV. Self-narrative\n\"I tan, I don't burn\" may push\nhim to Type V/VI. Behavior-first\nrow copy is PARTIAL mitigation —\nhe reads \"rarely burns\" on V and\nself-selects on that clause alone.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s5gul9ewdir2b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 735,
      "y": 2495,
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "text": "Mid-stride tap. Grants.\nButton MUST visibly\nrespond (spinner /\nlocation.fill swap) —\n~2-5 sec fetch feels\nlike eternity in motion.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s5xsp0iqdn0m",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 995,
      "y": 2495,
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "text": "Reads TWO things:\nthe integer + tier color.\nEverything else is\nwasted screen real estate.\nSaccade does NOT reach\nthe L3 link.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s52g2afy2x4yt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1255,
      "y": 2495,
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "text": "Set app down at\ntrailhead. Now at\nmile 8. Hasn't looked\nat phone. Repeating-\nuse = nothing yet —\nuntil window elapses.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
