      "id": "mpcde2s5umarfteoej",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1515,
      "y": 2495,
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "text": "★ HIS SAFETY MOMENT ★\nWindow-elapsed: hero swaps\nto 🛡 + warning haptic. THE\nWHOLE APP IS JUSTIFIED BY\nTHIS STATE FIRING CORRECTLY\nFOR HIM. Verify haptic +\nvisual contrast in direct sun.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.421Z",
      "version": 1
