      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.284Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.284Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcey3ngzhfrvjxfum",
      "type": "arrow",
      "x": 650,
      "y": 1540,
      "width": 80,
      "height": -800,
      "strokeColor": "#F57F17",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.284Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.284Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcey3ngq8ysxv6j1bg",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 475,
      "y": 1580,
      "strokeColor": "#5D4037",
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "L1 modal still re-fires every cold launch.\nThe yellow NowView banner is the reach-back\nsurface when the photosensitizer loop is active.\n\nNo special-category-data toggle.\nNo \"Don't Show Again.\"",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.284Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.284Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcey3ngukg8vvrsrm",
      "type": "arrow",
      "x": 1050,
      "y": 1540,
      "width": -410,
      "height": -694,
      "strokeColor": "#F57F17",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.284Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.284Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcey3ng965bm3a0ekh",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 875,
      "y": 1580,
      "strokeColor": "#5D4037",
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "If model output ≥ 240 minutes, the hero number\nDISPLAYS \"240+ min\" rather than the literal\ninteger.\n\nThe cap now lives inside the portrait hero card,\nnot a desktop-style side panel.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.284Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.284Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcey3nhpv9u3t0mj7j",
      "type": "arrow",
      "x": 1450,
      "y": 1540,
      "width": -750,
      "height": -456,
      "strokeColor": "#F57F17",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.285Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.285Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcey3nhju2eo2fvxh",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1275,
      "y": 1580,
      "strokeColor": "#5D4037",
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "Attribution sits in the UV secondary card\nright below the hero and stays visible in the\nsame portrait viewport.\n\n\"Source: Apple Weather\" stays on-screen\nwherever Apple Weather data is shown.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.285Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.285Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcey3nhndi3kjxmu4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 75,
      "y": 1785,
      "strokeColor": "#1a1a1a",
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "📌  VERDICT-CARD LEARN-MORE DEEP-LINK",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.285Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.285Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcey3nhhv9a4tm2w3t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 75,
      "y": 1810,
      "strokeColor": "#5D4037",
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "Inline caveat on the hero card carries the\nlearn-more deep-link into AboutView\n(anchor = `notForMe`).\n\nThis keeps the iPhone layout stacked while\npreserving the L3 reach-back pattern.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.285Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.285Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
